Add a rule from a URL

Usage: moss rules add [OPTIONS] <URL>

Arguments:
  <URL>  URL to download the rule from

Options:
      --global     Install to global rules (~/.config/moss/rules/) instead of project
      --json       Output as JSON
      --jq <EXPR>  Filter JSON output with jq expression (implies --json)
      --pretty     Human-friendly output with colors and formatting
      --compact    Compact output without colors (overrides TTY detection)
  -h, --help       Print help
